data.description: Second Chance at calling this Beauty Home! Buyer's financing fell through so don't waste this new opportunity. Welcome to your new home in Marrero!! The Potential is unlimited with this hidden gem sitting on a corner lot with rear yard access and a great backyard entertaining spot!  This Precious homes offers 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms, as well as a nice living area that opens to the dining and kitchen areas. If you are looking for a very well maintained home in a X Flood Zone, you don't want to miss viewing this property today!!
